text:
Is log4j.jar vversion 1.2.15 compatible with JDK 1.5 ?
What is new version of log4j.jar? Is this compatible with JDK 1.5

All versions of Log4j 1.2.x work with JDK1.3+, so yes.  JDK1.5 is supported.  Closing this as invalid as questions should go to the log4j-user email list, not Bugzilla.

Jake
